data.description: Welcome to 2451 Dawn Dr, a meticulously designed and remodeled home.  This exquisite property offers a perfect blend of modern luxury, privacy and convenience.  It features a beautiful, modern remodeled kitchen with stainless appliances including natural gas range.  A 3 car boat deep garage, RV parking large enough to add an RV garage and private entertainers backyard with sparkling pool with spill pots and BBQ area are perfect for a modern comfortable and private lifestyle.  You will love the coziness of the great room, recently remodeled kitchen with quartz countertops, stainless gas range and refrigerator.  The master suite features dual sinks and walk-in closet.  This split bedrooms floor plan has the guest bedrooms and newly remodeled bath on the other side of the home for privacy.  The neighborhood amenities include location on the lake side of the highway, underground utilities, private community park and community sewer included in the HOA fees.  Whether you are a boating enthusiast, love outdoor activities or simply enjoy the beauty of the Arizona desert, the home offers the perfect setting.
